column1: Observer formerly at Tilford Highmead Stn No 187/4/7
1951 Feb Incorrect Observer refuses to accept correction
1955 Feb 25 Inspection Can leaks Measure certified Gauge o/s Recommend moving gauge 20ft NE
1955 Mar Gauge moved to position recomended
1957 Station renamed Farnham Bells Piece. No change of site
Post 1960 known as Farnham Bells Piece  SRC_ID 6344
